OL,3,CMan sentenced to 23 years for shooting
OL,4,Cvictim at Britain's highest pub
OL,6,FA man who shot another man at
OL,7,FBritain's highest pub has been
OL,8,Fsentenced to 23 years for his actions.
OL,10,FRichard Bowser fired four bullets at
OL,11,Fhis victim at the Tan Hill Inn in
OL,12,FSwaledale, North Yorkshire, on 21 July
OL,13,Flast year after physically assaulting
OL,14,Fstaff and other customers inside the
OL,15,Fpub.
OL,17,FA court heard how the 46-year-old
OL,18,Fforced the victim into a toilet before
OL,19,Fshooting at him from behind a locked
OL,20,Fdoor as he tried to flee.
