OL,3,CMan sentenced to 23 years for shooting
OL,4,Cvictim at Britain's highest pub
OL,6,FTwo bullets struck the victim in the
OL,7,Fchest, causing little damage, but
OL,8,Fanother hit him in the arm, where it
OL,9,Fremains lodged.
OL,11,FHe has been jailed for 19 years and
OL,12,Fwill serve four years on extended
OL,13,Flicence after he was found guilty of
OL,14,Fwounding with intent and two counts of
OL,15,Fpossession of a firearm with intent to
OL,16,Fendanger life at Teesside Crown Court.
OL,18,FBowser, of Worcester Place, Bishop
OL,19,FAuckland, had previously pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to assaulting three people and
OL,21,Fbeing in possession of a firearm.
