OL,3,CMan sentenced to 23 years for shooting
OL,4,Cvictim at Britain's highest pub
OL,6,FHe was found not guilty on two charges
OL,7,Fof attempted murder.
OL,9,FDuring the trial, the court heard that
OL,10,FBowser, who had been staying in one of
OL,11,Fthe pub's glamping pods, had struggled
OL,12,Fto pay for drinks when his card was
OL,13,Fdeclined, leading to a fight breaking
OL,14,Fout in the bar.
OL,16,FBowser hit other customers and staff
OL,17,Fmembers before being locked out of the
OL,18,Fpub. He went on to attack his victim
OL,19,Farmed with a revolver.
