OL,3,CMan sentenced to 23 years for shooting
OL,4,Cvictim at Britain's highest pub
OL,6,FDefending Alistair MacDonald KC said
OL,7,FBowser was ashamed of his behaviour
OL,8,Finside the bar and there was no
OL,9,Fsuggestion of prior planning.
OL,11,FThe court also heard how he has been a
OL,12,F"model prisoner" while on remand.
OL,14,FSentencing Judge Howard Crowson, said:
OL,15,F"It is clear from the verdicts of the
OL,16,Fjury, in my view, that you intended to
OL,17,Fendanger life or the lives of somebody
OL,18,Fother than (the victim).
