OL,3,CMan sentenced to 23 years for shooting
OL,4,Cvictim at Britain's highest pub
OL,6,F"Ultimately those convictions were
OL,7,Ffound on your comments at the police
OL,8,Fstation after arrest. During your time
OL,9,Fin custody, you wanted to explain why
OL,10,Fyou carried these firearms to a remote
OL,11,Fand peaceful inn on the Yorkshire
OL,12,Fmoors.
OL,14,F"You have a lengthy explanation which
OL,15,FI summarise as an account of a
OL,16,Fdeveloping feud in which you see your
OL,17,Fopponents as cowards resorting to gang
OL,18,Fattacks upon you.
