OL,3,CMan sentenced to 23 years for shooting
OL,4,Cvictim at Britain's highest pub
OL,6,F"You were recorded as saying 'you
OL,7,Fwon't have a proper fight, so that's
OL,8,Fwhy I took the guns cause I'm going to
OL,9,Fblow his head off'. You were saying
OL,10,F'you had a chance for a fight - I'm
OL,11,Fgoing to blow your head off'
OL,12,Fcontinuing with 'let me out and I'll
OL,13,Fkill the lot of them'."
OL,15,FBowser was jailed for eight years for
OL,16,Fwounding with intent and 11 years for
OL,17,Fthe firearm offences. He will serve
OL,18,Ffour years on extended licence
OL,19,Fconcurrently for the firearm offences.
